[normal] 
[normal]I am the manager of Sleat Community Trust, a community organisation in the south-west corner of the 
[normal]Isle of Skye
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]I am also a director of 
[normal]Community Land
[normal] 
[normal]Scotland
[normal]—a fairly new one at that.
[normal]Peter Peacock[bold]: I am Peter Peacock.
[normal] 
[normal]I work very part-time for 
[normal]Community Land
[normal] 
[normal]Scotland
[normal] as a policy advisor, and I should declare an interest, Chair, in that I was a co-writer of the report you published, 
[normal]“
[normal]432:50
