[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]but the only input from 
[normal]the Crown Estate 
[normal]was to 
[normal]sen
[normal]d
[normal] them a bill for the extra dues.
[normal] 
[normal]              
[normal]There are huge things in marine renewables going to be happening.
[normal] 
[normal]We are getting told as a community where it is going to happen
[normal] and
[normal] who is going to do it, and absolutely no input as to what the communities could earn out of that
[normal] and
[normal] 
[normal]whether the 
[normal]infrastructure could be used to do more than one thing
