[normal]Q27 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Mr Reid:[bold] [bold]Have you given any thought to how you would structure ownership of the seabed and once you go further out?
[normal]Peter Peacock[bold]: We have, to the extent of recognising that we think the foreshore should belong to the community that already owns the land adjacent to it.
[normal] 
[normal]Where that isn’t the case, we think the foreshore should go to the local authority in the local community interest.
[normal] 
