[normal]              
[normal]On the land issue generally, the one big—
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q66 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Chair:[bold] I think we have this. I am sure we appreciate there is a natural reluctance to point out to our Scottish Government colleagues the error of their ways in this as in so many other issues. I think we can make an exception here because it is so significant to lots of local communities.
